The,SURFnet,Open,Education,API,aka,Open,Onderwijs,API,is,an,open,standard,for,sharing,education,data,Its,production,has,been,spearheaded,by,SURFnet,in,collaboration,with,institutions,of,higher,learning,The,API,facilitates,the,sharing,of,wide,ranging,academic,information,including,courses,student,marks,course,credits,and,semester,schedules,Developers,in,turn,use,the,data,to,build,new,applications